# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_MODEL_ESTIMATED_MAX_SPEED

## Summary
Get the estimated top speed of the vehicle model on a flat surface

## Parameters
* **MODEL_NAMES** vehicleModelHashKey: VehicleModelName - model name of vehicle

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Useful links
- [VHub: Vehicles](https://vhub.wiki/vehicles)

## Notes
Returns max speed (without mods) of the specified vehicle model in m/s.
